title: Nasty

description.plain:
“Nasty” is the lead single from Tinashe’s seventh album QUANTUM BABY. The song was first previewed by Tinashe via Instagram live on February 14, 2024, as a Valentine’s Day gift for her fans.

After almost two months, the official release date was revealed with an announcement post on social media.

The song first gained huge attraction thanks to several videos made on TikTok and X in June 2024, that made the song go viral.

On June 18, 2024, Tinashe released the ‘Match My Freak’ extended play, comprising five remixes of ‘Nasty’. A month later, on July 19, 2024, she extended the EP by releasing two more remixes, one being titled ‘Nasty Girl Remix’ which featured the singer Chlöe and ‘Nasty XXX Remix’ which featured rapper Tyga.
